,&quot;sizes&quot;:[]},&quot;classic_row_gap_mobile&quot;:{&quot;unit&quot;:&quot;px&quot;,&quot;size&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;sizes&quot;:[]}}" data-widget_type="posts.classic"><div class="elementor-widget-container"><div class="elementor-posts-container elementor-posts elementor-posts--skin-classic elementor-grid"><article class="elementor-post elementor-grid-item post-7022 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-brio-news"> <a class="elementor-post__thumbnail__link" href="https://builtbybrio.com/bc-construction-labor-shortage-crisis-or-opportunity-in-2025/" tabindex="-1"><div class="elementor-post__thumbnail"><img loading="lazy" loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="2048" height="2048" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" data-src="https://builtbybrio.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Gemini_Generated_Image_2ji58u2ji58u2ji5.jpeg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-image-7024 lazyload" alt="Gemini Generated Image 2ji58u2ji58u2ji5" title="BC Construction Labor Shortage: Crisis or Opportunity in 2025? 15"><noscript><img loading="lazy" loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="2048" height="2048" src="https://builtbybrio.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Gemini_Generated_Image_2ji58u2ji58u2ji5.jpeg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-image-7024 lazyload" alt="Gemini Generated Image 2ji58u2ji58u2ji5" title="BC Construction Labor Shortage: Crisis or Opportunity in 2025? 16" srcset="https://builtbybrio.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Gemini_Generated_Image_2ji58u2ji58u2ji5.jpeg 2048w, https://builtbybrio.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Gemini_Generated_Image_2ji58u2ji58u2ji5-300x300.jpeg 300w, https://builtbybrio.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Gemini_Generated_Image_2ji58u2ji58u2ji5-1024x1024.jpeg 1024w, https://builtbybrio.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Gemini_Generated_Image_2ji58u2ji58u2ji5-150x150.jpeg 150w, https://builtbybrio.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Gemini_Generated_Image_2ji58u2ji58u2ji5-768x768.jpeg 768w, https://builtbybrio.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Gemini_Generated_Image_2ji58u2ji58u2ji5-1536x1536.jpeg 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 2048px) 100vw, 2048px" /></noscript></div> </a><div class="elementor-post__text"><h3 class="elementor-post__title"> <a href="https://builtbybrio.com/bc-construction-labor-shortage-crisis-or-opportunity-in-2025/"> BC Construction Labor Shortage: Crisis or Opportunity in 2025? </a></h3> <a class="elementor-post__read-more" href="https://builtbybrio.com/bc-construction-labor-shortage-crisis-or-opportunity-in-2025/" aria-label="Read more about BC Construction Labor Shortage: Crisis or Opportunity in 2025?" tabindex="-1"> Read More » </a></div></article><article class="elementor-post elementor-grid-item post-7014 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-brio-guides category-brio-news"> <a class="elementor-post__thumbnail__link" href="https://builtbybrio.com/the-bc-energy-step-code-is-here-to-stay-what-it-means-for-your-2025-home-renovation/" tabindex="-1"><div class="elementor-post__thumbnail"><img loading="lazy" loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="2048" height="2048" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" data-src="https://builtbybrio.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Gemini_Generated_Image_uz0naiuz0naiuz0n.jpeg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-image-7017 lazyload" alt="Gemini Generated Image uz0naiuz0naiuz0n" title="BC Construction Labor Shortage: Crisis or Opportunity in 2025? 17"><noscript><img loading="lazy" loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="2048" height="2048" src="https://builtbybrio.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Gemini_Generated_Image_uz0naiuz0naiuz0n.jpeg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-image-7017 lazyload" alt="Gemini Generated Image uz0naiuz0naiuz0n" title="BC Construction Labor Shortage: Crisis or Opportunity in 2025? 18" srcset="https://builtbybrio.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/Gemini_Generated_Ima